subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous lake is located in Udaipur?
question_hi: उदयपुर में कौन सी प्रमुखी कट है?
explanation_en: Fateh Sagar Lake and Udaipur Lake are man-made lakes, while Ranjit Sagar Lake and Pratap Sagar Lake are natural lakes. Ranjit Sagar Lake is located in Udaipur, making it the correct answer.
